title: Munchkin® Arm & Hammer Diaper Pail Refill Rings, 544 Count, 2 Pack (272 Count Each)
description: Smell the difference! Arm & Hammer lavender-scented refill rings does the dirty work by keeping odors out and locking that fresh smell in. Each 7-layer bag ring holds up to 272 newborn diapers, and keeps your nursery from smelling like - well - a nursery. Not compatible with the Arm & Hammer Diaper Pail by Munchkin.
